        "@value": "Future development zones' may only be determined as a consecutive zoning under Â§ 12 section 4 or in the case of rezonings, ruled in Â§ 23 sec. 2 lit. a, Code of Spatial Planning of Vorarlberg. Land, that is not suitable as building zones, must not be zoned in future development zones. Future development zones can be subdivided into core-, residential-, mixed- or operating areas. A distinction is made between category I and category II areas, which are designated for operating facilities."
