    "http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition": [
      {
        "@language": "de",
        "@value": "In Landwirtschaftsgebieten ist die Errichtung von GebÃ¤uden und Anlagen zulÃ¤ssig, soweit dies fÃ¼r die bodenabhÃ¤ngige land- und forstwirtschaftliche Nutzung einschlieÃlich der dazu gehÃ¶renden erforderlichen WohnrÃ¤ume und WohngebÃ¤ude und fÃ¼r Nebengewerbe der Land-und Forstwirtschaft sowie die hÃ¤usliche NebenbeschÃ¤ftigung notwendig ist."
      },
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "In agricultural areas, the construction of buildings and facilities is permitted, as far as it is necessary in terms of the soil-dependent agricultural and silvicultural use, including the associated, necessary residential spaces and residential buildings and for the subsidiary occupation of agriculture and silviculture as well as the domestic external activity."
